1 - check_proxy_lb.ksh
-----------------------

    a) Description

        This plugin is use to check availability of AJP over the web page of Apache's module: mod_proxy_balancer.

    b) Prerequisites

        - ksh
        - wget
        - curl

    c) Usage

         ./check_proxy_lb.ksh --help
		 
2 - check_ad.vbs

    a) Description

	    This plugin is use to check Active Directory with NRPE, the original plugin come from 
        http://exchange.nagios.org/directory/Plugins/Operating-Systems/Windows/Active-Directory-%28AD%29-Check/details
		I have added French language support with the detection of the page code (for the accented characters)
		
	c) Prerequisites
	
		- Support Tools (dcdiag.exe)
